959
00:57:27.412 --> 00:57:30.672
I'm going to show you the results, and this is where I think AI can be helpful.

960
00:57:30.852 --> 00:57:34.192
AI might at least be reproducible.

961
00:57:34.252 --> 00:57:36.292
You can see here that

962
00:57:37.632 --> 00:57:38.732
they didn't always agree

963
00:57:39.952 --> 00:57:43.932
when they interpreted the same case in phase two with the diagnosis they had

964
00:57:43.992 --> 00:57:45.612
given in phase one.

965
00:57:53.172 --> 00:57:56.692
Because canaries were mentioned earlier, I want to show a picture of a pigeon.

966
00:57:58.052 --> 00:58:01.012
Pigeons are trainable observers of images,

967
00:58:01.852 --> 00:58:05.652
and in just two weeks, with reinforcement feeding, as

968
00:58:05.712 --> 00:58:09.512
shown with the food pellets on the left, they can be taught, this is

969
00:58:09.552 --> 00:58:13.472
two weeks, with fairly high accuracy to

970
00:58:13.532 --> 00:58:16.912
peck whether it's breast cancer or not on these images.

971
00:58:18.392 --> 00:58:22.372
If you attended this morning's plenary, you can see now AI can

972
00:58:22.412 --> 00:58:23.392
do this in minutes.

973
00:58:25.012 --> 00:58:26.172
So let's move into AI.

974
00:58:28.512 --> 00:58:31.932
Probably 15 years ago, I started collaborating with engineers.

975
00:58:32.092 --> 00:58:35.872
I would give them image data. They would then detect the

