1181
01:10:43.530 --> 01:10:46.830
This can only work if it's driven by centrally

1182
01:10:46.850 --> 01:10:50.770
government-funded research, or funding, because it's very hard for it

1183
01:10:50.870 --> 01:10:54.550
to defend, with the possible exception of the vaccine

1184
01:10:54.970 --> 01:10:55.250
model.

1185
01:10:55.370 --> 01:10:57.270
I think so. I think government's needed there, too.

1186
01:10:57.470 --> 01:10:57.650
Yeah.

1187
01:10:58.450 --> 01:10:58.870
Absolutely.

1188
01:11:01.410 --> 01:11:05.310
I think vaccines are kind of the poster child of

1189
01:11:05.370 --> 01:11:09.270
not being able to get anywhere because at the point where they're starting

1190
01:11:09.370 --> 01:11:10.610
to show some efficacy,

1191
01:11:11.510 --> 01:11:15.430
pharmaceuticals are not so interested in the type of vaccines

1192
01:11:15.490 --> 01:11:19.370
you give three times and never use again or end up

1193
01:11:19.380 --> 01:11:23.360
using once a year. There might be some interest in those highly

1194
01:11:23.490 --> 01:11:27.370
personalized vaccines that are being given almost like a therapeutic,

1195
01:11:27.430 --> 01:11:29.170
where people are getting them all the time.

1196
01:11:29.750 --> 01:11:32.750
But these are very low-cost

1197
01:11:32.950 --> 01:11:36.850
interventions, and I think that governments

1198
01:11:36.910 --> 01:11:39.470
have to step in as a health

1199
01:11:40.450 --> 01:11:41.850
service, health improvement.

1200
01:11:43.970 --> 01:11:44.060
Thanks. Joanne?

1201
01:11:44.650 --> 01:11:47.510
On the topic of how to get more funding,

1202
01:11:48.470 --> 01:11:51.790
I run a training program. It's called The Clinical Scholars Program.

1203
01:11:51.870 --> 01:11:54.930
It's a follow-up of the Robert Wood Johnson Clinical Scholars Program,

1204
01:11:55.870 --> 01:11:59.130
and I realize that part of our curriculum needs to be communication.

1205
01:12:00.250 --> 01:12:02.550
We scientists have done a terrible job.

1206
01:12:04.370 --> 01:12:05.790
We need to learn how to frame.

1207
01:12:06.890 --> 01:12:10.080
We need to learn about the power of the clinical vignette,

1208
01:12:11.710 --> 01:12:15.560
and it's hard. And so I think going forward, part of

1209
01:12:15.630 --> 01:12:18.470
